title: Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea S04E20 Man-Beast AVI

Episode 20, Airdate: February 18, 1968
"MAN-BEAST"

The Seaview's crew deals with a Jekyll-Hyde crisis: Crane (David Hedison) is periodically changing into a raving monster.

Nelson: Richard Basehart. Morton: Bob Dowdell. Kowalski: Del Monroe. Sharkey: Terry Becker. Braddock: Lawrence Montaigne.
